						               													<description>Truth cards are a new board game from the developers of the Conflict Card. In this game, you will learn the whole truth about yourself from your friends, as well as reveal the truth about other players in the game. Be ready to learn a lot of new things about yourself, sometimes even unpleasant. Laughter will accompany you all game. Vote, who jokes don't reach the first time, and who needs to tie with food pics. Whose snoring can be tortured by prisoners of war, and who is the most accessible girl in the company. Who looks much older than their age, and who would agree to marry for the sake of EU citizenship. Who has the most disgusting voice, and who is already sick of everyone with their dumb jokes. All this is funny, and in some places, you should open the hard truth by playing the Truth cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The rules are simple. In the beginning of the game players choose their avatars and also receive voting cards with avatars of other players. On each turn players read questions from the card. Players are voting for other players by placing voting cards which is best describe some other player by this question. The winner of voting receives question card (1 point) and players receive their voting cards back. Player who receive the most points is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
